content:
Give Users Access to Case Feed Through Custom Profiles

Available in: Salesforce Classic (not available in all orgs)
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

To create and edit profiles: Manage Profiles and Permission Sets

To give users access:
Create a profile.
On the Profile page, click Edit.
In General User Permissions, select Use Case Feed.
Click Save.
Assign users to the profile.
title: Configuring Access to Service Cloud Case Feed
